These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, airplane, snowmobile
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Transport   | snowmobile | airplane | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
House: tower, wooden, ranch-style
1. the wooden house is in an odd position##4
2. the tower house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| House   | tower | ranch-style | wooden |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, june, august
1. the person who's birthday is in june is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Birthday   | october | june | august |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, yellow, aquamarine
1. the person who likes yellow is in an odd position##4
