.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-20::.
City: nizza, berlin, prague
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to nizza is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| City   | berlin | prague | nizza |

 